      "path": "README.md",
      "content": "# CSV Parser

This is a simple CSV parser written in TypeScript.

## Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/csv-parser.git
cd csv-parser
tsc
```

## Usage

### Parse CSV File

```bash
node dist/cli.js parse --input path/to/file.csv
```

### Get Stats for CSV File

```bash
node dist/cli.js stats --input path/to/file.csv
```
"
    },
    {
      "path": "package.json",
      "content": "{
  "name": "csv-parser",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "A simple CSV parser written in TypeScript",
  "main": "dist/cli.js",
  "scripts": {
    "build": "tsc",
    "test": "node --test tests/oracle.test.js"
  },
  "keywords": [
    "csv",
    "parser",
    "typescript"
